answers.body_markdown:
The permissions issue was caused by the `&lt;location&gt;` tag in the `web.config`. The `&lt;system.webServer&gt;&lt;validation&gt;` tag did not like being wrapped in the `&lt;location&gt;` tag so I pulled it out;
like this.
```
  &lt;system.webServer&gt;
    &lt;validation validateIntegratedModeConfiguration=&quot;false&quot; /&gt;
  &lt;/system.webServer&gt;
  
&lt;location path=&quot;.&quot; inheritInChildApplications=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
  &lt;system.webServer&gt;
	...
```
Now all of the folders are readable.

